The paper also discusses wiretap channels, which is a topic in Cryptography and Security (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper mentions multi-carrier transmission systems, cognitive multiple access, and relay networks, which are topics in Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) and Systems and Control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper briefly touches upon code construction, which is a topic in Multimedia (cs.MM).
